article_id:1536,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding Gifts for Fixing an Issue,image_path:,message:<div>The following issue was fixed in version 1.23.0, which was released around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1598497200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Issue Details</div><div>・When used as a shared skill, the effects of adventurer Gala Luca&#39;s Shining Slash skill apply to the adventurer Tiki&#39;s Divine Dragon skill Breath of Fog.</div><div><br></div><div>Along with the fix for this issue, starting <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1598590800"></span>, we will send the light tomes required to unlock the Shining Slash shared skill (six light tomes) to players who unlocked the Shining Slash shared skill up until update 1.22.1.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1598583600,update_time1598526080